ssidident
Conrad Lara <kg6jei@amsat.org>

ssidident send a beacon packet out at ~500ms interval on the wireless (monitor mode) interface it has been attached to.

This program was designed for the Broadband-Hamnnet project to ensure compliance with rules about identification.

This program also allows for remote aiming into a specific node when used alongside aimer.

Usage is ssidident INTERFACE

Based on:
Packetspammer
Andy Green <andy@warmcat.com>
